    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in total mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just left the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s super clean and drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feel without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for this to go to a great home, so feel free to message me if you\u2019re interested!",
