    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L inline-six features crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies, with the dual-VANOS system operating flawlessly across the entire power band. Mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain delivers linear power to a variable M-differential. Mechanically, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and rod bearing service is documented, ensuring long-term structural and internal integrity. The chassis remains taut, utilizing factory-spec suspension geometry that offers unparalleled steering feedback. With original paint depth and a cabin devoid of bolster wear or pixel failure, this is a turn-key specimen for the serious collector.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
