    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of rock chips, swirls, or blemishes, while the interior remains in showroom condition, featuring supple, uncreased leather and a cabin that still carries a hint of the factory scent. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, backed by a comprehensive binder of maintenance records. It delivers a driving experience that is tight, responsive, and indistinguishable from new. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a virtually flawless example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
