      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute dream of a car! Honestly, it\u2019s in such stunning shape that you'd swear it just rolled off the showroom floor yesterday. It has been incredibly well-loved and pampered, and it drives as smooth as butter. If you've been looking for that perfect, like-new feel without the brand-new sticker price, this is definitely the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
