      "description": "This 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. Featuring the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six, this unit delivers 385 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical profile is flawless, boasting Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a limited-slip differential for superior lateral grip. A recent DME report confirms zero overrevs in all ranges, and the cooling system has been overhauled with a new water pump and low-temp thermostat. The chassis is impeccably clean, with all bushings, CV boots, and Brembo monoblock calipers in like-new condition. An investment-grade example for the serious driver.",
